{
  "stem": "14251.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She usually is a wealth of data, but she couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day that was the end of Michael.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Michael's father was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, there was a little girl named Bela.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, in Europe, that's either a boy or a girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Suddenly, Bela was missing, and I remember Bela and parents coming to our place on a Sunday for coffee or something, when that was still possible.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And those were the only two people that I can recall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it's all-- when you're someone growing up, it's all a natural-- you think this is how the world is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You don't-- I don't think you suffer the way your parents suffer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know how I feel when my daughter's in some kind of distress, or any family member.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's because I'm an adult, and I, therefore, have the ability to feel that stress.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It must have been very hard not to transfer a lot of these things to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But fortunately, for the European upbringing style, that already was out of the question.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You wouldn't share that kind of data with your children, or any significant data, until it became necessary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They insisted then that I had to share certain data with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would describe my religious background as zip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means I went to a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only knew Jewish people as long as they were still there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was as a cautionary thing that my grandfather-- my mother's father-- and my parents decided this could not perpetuate that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you were only doing it at home by then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Couldn't be out at strange hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] What if we did get to go underground?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
